  "description": "ORGANISM's cellular automata engine generates non-repeating LFO-like population wave outputs that drive OVERTONE's pitch via LFOToPitch coupling. The continued-fraction spectral engine wobbles at rates and shapes determined by the rule set of the cellular colony — not by a waveform oscillator. Change org_ruleSet to change the modulation character entirely. The colony pilots the timbre.",
